#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Possible use of an untrusted Live system found on local hard-disk\"]]\n"
msgstr ""
"[[!meta title=\"Possible ús d'un sistema Live no fiable trobat al disc dur "
"local\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!pagetemplate template=\"news.tmpl\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!pagetemplate template=\"news.tmpl\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!tag security/fixed]]\n"
msgstr "[[!tag security/fixed]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"live-initramfs boot scripts, that are used in amnesia, can boot an untrusted "
"Live system found on the local hard-disk, rather than the one present on the "
"USB stick on CD, as could be expected."
msgstr ""
"Els scripts d'arrencada live-initramfs, que s'utilitzen a amnesia, poden "
"arrencar un sistema Live no fiable que es troba al disc dur local, en lloc "
"del present al llapis USB o CD, com era d'esperar."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This can only happen in the (pretty rare) case when Linux needs more than 15 "
"seconds to make the legitimate USB stick or CD ready."
msgstr ""
"Això només pot passar en el cas (poc probable) quan Linux necessita més de "
"15 segons per preparar el llapis USB o el CD legítims."

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Impact"
msgstr "Impacte"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Booting another Live system than the one you think, without being told, can "
"lead to any kind of information leak, anonymity break, etc."
msgstr ""
"L'arrencada d'un altre sistema Live que no sigui el que creieu, sense que us "
"ho diguin, pot provocar qualsevol tipus de filtració d'informació, "
"trencament d'anonimat, etc."

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Solution"
msgstr "Solució"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"None yet. Either build your own images from Git, or wait for the imminent "
"0.4.2 release."
msgstr ""
"Cap encara. Creeu les vostres pròpies imatges des de Git o espereu la "
"imminent versió 0.4.2."

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mitigation"
msgstr "Mitigació"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Do not use amnesia on untrusted computers."
msgstr "No utilitzeu amnesia en ordinadors no fiables."

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Affected versions"
msgstr "Versions afectades"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Any Debian Live-based system, including every amnesia release until, and "
"including, 0.4.1."
msgstr ""
"Qualsevol sistema basat en Debian Live, inclosos tots els llançaments "
"d'amnesia fins, i inclòs, 0.4.1."
